</P>
<P>
   A4141 BC-QUOTE-OF-THE-DAY-NYT 86 21:24 R A
</P>
<P>
   QUOTATION OF THE DAY &QL;
</P>
<P>
   A4139 BC-HEART-SURGERY-SPI 1029 21:23 U A
</P>
<P>
   CONTROVERSIAL `BATISTA PROCEDURE' HEART SURGERY PERFORMED IN
SEATTLE &QL;
