   COXNET WHEELS 0427 _ Extra doors are the big deal these days for
trucks and vans, and Ford has taken that concept to the max with
the '99 Ranger compact pickup. Just add $660 to the purchase price,
and the hot-selling Ranger becomes a four-door vehicle. (DeVault,
