<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-SCHIZOPHRENIA-HELP28-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    New hope for schizophrenia's bewildered victims
 &HT;    By Patrick Beach
 &HT;    c. 1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
