<P>
   &UR; IN SEARCH OF THE ELUSIVE MEGAPLUME &LR;  &QL; 
 &UR; FOUR COLOR SLIDES ARE AVAILABLE FREE &QL; 
 &UR; (1,100 words with a 200-word sidebar) &QL; 
 &UR; By JOSH FISCHMAN &LR;  &QC;
</P>
<P>
   Imagine underwater volcanoes that erupt with giant twisting
plumes filled with microbes and other life that spin dervishly like
aquatic hurricanes. Welcome to the strange, almost completely
unknown life of undersea eruptions and what oceanographers are
beginning to learn about theses Vesuvians of the deep.
</P>
<P>
   slugged: BC-UNDERSTANDING-MEGAPLUMES-NYTSF. Sent to category
codes ``a'' general news and ``l'' lifestyle news.
