<P>
   KOSOVO-CONGRESS (Washington) _ Over objections from Republican
congressional leaders and the Clinton administration, the House
will formally vote on the Kosovo conflict Wednesday. The votes are
being forced by Rep. Tom Campbell, R-Calif., whose resolutions call
for either declaring war or withdrawing U.S. forces. By JENNIFER
