<P>
   JAPAN-U.S. (Tokyo) _ The lower house of Parliament on Tuesday
passed crucial legislation to improve military cooperation with the
United States, smoothing the way for Prime Minister Keizo Obuchi's
departure Thursday for a summit meeting with President Clinton. By
Nicholas D. Kristof.
</P>
<P>
   INDONESIA-TIMOR (Bangkok) _ President B.J. Habibie of Indonesia
