<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    GORE CITES FAMILY'S HISTORY IN BID FOR BLACK SUPPORT
 &HT;    Moving in (w) Washington and (p) politics categories.
 &HT;    By SCOTT SHEPARD
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
