<P>
   FORD RANGER: Extra doors are the big deal these days for trucks
and vans, and Ford has taken that concept to the max with the '99
Ranger compact pickup. Just add $660 to the purchase price, and the
hot-selling Ranger becomes a four-door vehicle. (Includes 3-column
color photo of a Ranger Sport Supercab, 2-column color photo of
Ranger Sport Supercab's interior and 1-column detail photo of
