</P>
<P>
   WITH: AT A GLANCE: Fact box previewing the 1999 Ford Ranger
Sport Supercab.
</P>
<P>
   WITH: SHARP DRIVING: It has rubber floor mats, no air bags, no
5-mph bumpers and a sticker price of $97,100. I've never felt safer
in any vehicle in my life. What is it? It's a Hummer, of course.
When offered the opportunity to test-drive the Hummer, I
halfheartedly accepted. But after a week with my competition yellow
civilian version of the same vehicle that our troops are using
around the world, I came away a fan.(Includes 1-column color
photograph of columnist.)
</P>
