erotic. In truth, it's basically a small town that marries Euro
ultra mod and Old World quaintness, with residents who display both
Continental savoir-faire and British civility.
</P>
<P>
   ICELAND BEAUTY: Icelanders apparently do not feel the urge, as
Americans do, to put up billboards telling tourists where all the
cool stuff is. It's not hidden, but you have to know where to look.
</P>
<P>
   WITH: TRAVEL BRIEFS: If you would like to rent a luxury car in
London, Avis has inaugurated a program that it says can guarantee
you the make and model you want within 24 hours of your request.
