<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-04-27 16:41 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5175 &Cx1f; ttj-z
u k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-MEANS-COLUMN-HNS &LR;      04-27 0764
