daughter, now 26. ``Anybody that knows her knows she'd give you the
shirt off her back, but she'll tell you off in a heartbeat. That's
the kind of attitude that makes a helicopter pilot,'' he said.
First Lt. Mandy MacWhirter, an Azle High School graduate with a
