COLO-SHOOTING-SHRINE-1, 4-27 -- The parked pickup truck of shooting
victim John Tomlin is covered with flowers and messages on Tuesday.
Thousands of flowers, posters, and messages have been left near
Columbine High School where 12 students and a teacher were slain
last week by two students who committed suicide in the school
following their shooting rampage. (Monica Almeida/New York Times
Photo)
</P>
<P>
   (NYT15) WASHINGTON -- April 27, 1999 -- ADV. FOR SUN., MAY 2 --
DOLLHOUSES-COX-2, 4-27 -- A miniature doll sits at a sewing machine
in a bedroom of the ``American Country House,'' one of four doll
houses donated to the National Society Daughters of the American
