the PLO to declare statehood next week during a demonstration
outside Palestinian leader Yasser Arafat's office on Tuesday.
Arafat convened the PLO leadership on Tuesday to decide whether to
declare a Palestinian state on May 4 or extend peace talks with
Israel for another year. (Rina Castelnuovo/New York Times Photo)
</P>
