<SLUG> BC-PUBLIC-LIVES-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
FOR NOW, MAYOR LOSES HIS GRIP  
 GLAMOUR AMID THE STACKS 
BACKSTAGE WITH HARE
</HEADLINE>
   (mk) 
 By JAMES BARRON   
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   NEW YORK _ Mayor Rudolph Giuliani will not be doing any
gladhanding for a while.
</P>
<P>
   The mayor, it seems, injured his hand while _ what else? _
shaking hands.
</P>
