<DATE_TIME> 1999-04-27 23:14 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5813 &Cx1f; tib-z
u k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-DOWD-COLUMN-1STLD-WRI     04-27 0736
